frml:
FRML <> INFECTION_RATE        = RATE_CONTACT * PROBABILITY_TRANSMISION * INFECTIOUS(-1) / POPULATION(-1) $
FRML <> NEW_EXPOSED           = INFECTION_RATE * SUSCEPTIBLE + EXO_EXPOSED $
FRML <> EXPOSED=EXPOSED(-1)+(NEW_EXPOSED - NEW_INFECTIOUS)$
FRML <> NEW_INFECTIOUS        = NEW_EXPOSED(-2)*0.8 + NEW_EXPOSED(-3)*0.2  $
FRML <> NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER      = NEW_INFECTIOUS * NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER_RATE $
FRML <> EXIT_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER     = NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER(-14) $
FRML <> NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_HOSPITAL     = NEW_INFECTIOUS * (1-NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER_RATE) $
FRML <> INFECTIOUS=INFECTIOUS(-1)+(NEW_INFECTIOUS - EXIT_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER-EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER -EXIT_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER -EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD)$
FRML <> NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER        =  NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_HOSPITAL * NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER_RATE $
FRML <> EXIT_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER       = NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER(-5) $
FRML <> HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER=HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER(-1)+(NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER - EXIT_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER)$
FRML <> NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_INTENSIVE      =  NEW_INFECTIOUS_TO_HOSPITAL * (1-NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER_RATE) $
FRML <> NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER       = NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_INTENSIVE * NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER_RATE  $
FRML <> EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER      = NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER(-7) $
FRML <> INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER=INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER(-1)+(NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER-EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER)$
FRML <> NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD          = NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_INTENSIVE * (1-NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER_RATE)               $
FRML <> EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD         = NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD(-20) $
FRML <> INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD=INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD(-1)+(NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD-EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD)$
FRML <> HOSPITAL_NON_ICU=HOSPITAL_NON_ICU(-1)+(NEW_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER - EXIT_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER)$
FRML <> HOSPITAL_ICU=HOSPITAL_ICU(-1)+(NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER+NEW_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD-(EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER+EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD))$
FRML <> HOSPITAL                = HOSPITAL_NON_ICU+HOSPITAL_ICU $
FRML <> DEAD=DEAD(-1)+(EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_DEAD)$
FRML <> SUSCEPTIBLE=SUSCEPTIBLE(-1)+(-NEW_EXPOSED)$
FRML <> RECOVERED=RECOVERED(-1)+(EXIT_INFECTIOUS_TO_RECOVER + EXIT_INTENSIVE_TO_RECOVER + EXIT_HOSPITAL_TO_RECOVER)$
FRML <> POPULATION=POPULATION(-1)+(-((DEAD)-(DEAD(-1))))$
FRML <> DEAD_DELTA            = ((DEAD)-(DEAD(-1))) $
FRML <> INFECTIOUS_DELTA      = ((INFECTIOUS)-(INFECTIOUS(-1))) $
FRML <> HOSPITAL_DELTA        = ((HOSPITAL)-(HOSPITAL(-1))) $
FRML <> HOSPITAL_ICU_DELTA    = ((HOSPITAL_ICU)-(HOSPITAL_ICU(-1))) $
FRML <> DEAD_GROWTH            = 100 * DEAD_DELTA / DEAD(-1) $
FRML <> INFECTIOUS_GROWTH      = 100 * INFECTIOUS_DELTA / INFECTIOUS(-1) $
FRML <> HOSPITAL_GROWTH        = 100 * HOSPITAL_DELTA / HOSPITAL(-1) $
FRML <> HOSPITAL_ICU_GROWTH    = 100 * HOSPITAL_ICU_DELTA / HOSPITAL_ICU(-1) $
